      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-max        to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           add       w-lin-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione numero d'ordine del- *
      *                          * la prima riga appartenente alla pa- *
      *                          * gina (attuale + 1)                  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           add       w-lin-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se la prossima pagina e' sicuramen- *
      *                          * te prima dell'ultima                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    <    w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001
                     move  w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002
                                          to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac
                     go to acc-cor-reg-000.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si e' sull'ultima pagina la qua- *
      *                          * le e' pero' completamente piena     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           if        w-cat-rig-max        =    w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001
                     move  w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002
                                          to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac
                     go to acc-cor-reg-000.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si supera l'ultima pagina        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "+"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-cor      .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-997.
       acc-cor-reg-980.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Prsc da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-981.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rig-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-982.
       acc-cor-reg-981.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-982.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si e' sulla prima pagina         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    not  > w-lin-num-lin-vis
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-cor
                     go to acc-cor-reg-997.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se non si e' sulla prima pagina     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-lin-num-lin-vis    from w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-985.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Slct da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-986.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rig-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il numero riga di destinazione   *
      *                          * risulta oltre il numero d'ordine    *
      *                          * attuale si sottrae 1 al numero ri-  *
      *                          * ga di destinazione                  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-slc-num-rig    >    w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac
                     subtract  1          from w-cnt-slc-num-rig      .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-987.
       acc-cor-reg-986.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-987.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Ad accettazione nr riga selezionato *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-slc-num-rig    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-988.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf1 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Salvataggio video attuale               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione dati identificativi ordine *
      *                      * fornitore                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RO"                 to   l-dup-rof-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/orc/prg/obj/porc300b"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-dup-rof
                                               w-prs
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su esito operazione            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        l-dup-rof-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-988a.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Set del flag di trattamento ordine da   *
      *                      * duplicare                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   l-dup-rof-flg-orf      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Assestamento flag di visualizzazione    *
      *                      * prompts                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata *
      *                      * a zero per forzare la rivisualizzazione *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
       acc-cor-reg-988a.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ripristino video precedentemente salva- *
      *                      * to                                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Rimozione record dalla catena           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-988b.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf2 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Salvataggio video attuale               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione dati identificativi ordine *
      *                      * da evadere                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RO"                 to   l-eva-frc-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/orc/prg/obj/porc300f"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-eva-frc
                                               w-prs
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su esito operazione            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        l-eva-frc-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-989.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Set del flag di trattamento ordine da   *
      *                      * duplicare                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   l-eva-frc-flg-orc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Assestamento flag di visualizzazione    *
      *                      * prompts                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata *
      *                      * a zero per forzare la rivisualizzazione *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
       acc-cor-reg-989.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ripristino video precedentemente salva- *
      *                      * to                                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Rimozione record dalla catena           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-990.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf4 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Salvataggio area catena                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig            to   w-sav-cat-rig          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura record precedente dalla catena  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RD"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           subtract  1                    from w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a  *
      *                      * work di lavoro                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Normalizzazione valori precedenti riga  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-rig-val-aep (2)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ripristino area catena                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-sav-cat-rig        to   w-cat-rig              .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Movimento da work di lavoro a buffer    *
      *                      * catena movimenti                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig                to   w-cat-rig-buf          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Visualizzazione dati per riga di accet- *
      *                      * tazione                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-rig-cor-000      thru vis-rig-cor-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Normalizzazione status di impostazione  *
      *                      * riga                                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rig      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo impostazione : altri campi riga    *
      *                      * corpo                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   w-cnt-mfu-tip-imp      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad accettazione data consegna richiesta *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cor-reg-310.
       acc-cor-reg-995.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Pf3 da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Salvataggio video attuale               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione dati identificativi ordine *
      *                      * da duplicare                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RO"                 to   l-dup-rdo-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/orc/prg/obj/porc300e"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-dup-rdo
                                               w-prs
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su esito operazione            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        l-dup-rdo-exi-sts    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-996.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Set del flag di trattamento ordine da   *
      *                      * duplicare                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   l-dup-rdo-flg-orc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Assestamento flag di visualizzazione    *
      *                      * prompts                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata *
      *                      * a zero per forzare la rivisualizzazione *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-cor-nrp-vis      .
       acc-cor-reg-996.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ripristino video precedentemente salva- *
      *                      * to                                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Rimozione record dalla catena           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
           go to     acc-cor-reg-000.
       acc-cor-reg-997.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento status di impostazione corpo       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-max        =    zero
                     move  spaces         to   w-cnt-sts-imp-cor
           else      move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-cor      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Abblencamento note in righe documento           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   w-vis-not-rgd-top      .
           perform   vis-not-rgd-000      thru vis-not-rgd-999        .
       acc-cor-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione pagina corpo numero : w-cnt-cor-nrp-dav   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cor-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate, escluse fincature        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      06                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       vis-cor-reg-150.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero d'ordine del primo numero *
      *              * riga da visualizzare                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrp-dav    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           subtract  w-lin-num-lin-vis    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero d'ordine dell'ultimo nu-  *
      *              * mero riga da visualizzare                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
           add       w-lin-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione numero pagina in corso di trat- *
      *              * tamento                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cor-reg-npg-000  thru vis-cor-reg-npg-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Operazione di Start su catena movimenti         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start errata : fine visualizzazione      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-cor-reg-999.
       vis-cor-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale catena movimenti            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fine lettura : fine visualizzazione      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-cor-reg-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work di  *
      *              * lavoro                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riga singolo movimento                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero riga da visualizzare          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se oltre ultima riga da visualizzare       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    not  > w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009
                     go to vis-cor-reg-200.
       vis-cor-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione pagina corpo                              *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Numero pagina corpo                                       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cor-reg-npg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero di pagina                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione pagina attuale               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cat-rig-max
                                        giving w-cnt-cor-pag-max
                                     remainder w-cnt-cor-pag-rem      .
           if        w-cnt-cor-pag-rem    >    zero
                     add 1                to   w-cnt-cor-pag-max      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009
                                        giving w-cnt-cor-pag-att      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing pagina attuale                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-att    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-cnt-cor-pag-ep1      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing pagina finale                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-max    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-cnt-cor-pag-ep2      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-cor-pag-npa      .
           string    "["
                                delimited by   size
                     w-cnt-cor-pag-ep1
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "/"
                                delimited by   size
                     w-cnt-cor-pag-ep2
                                delimited by   spaces
                     "]"
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-cnt-cor-pag-npa      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Allineamento al centro                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      09                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-npa    to   w-all-str-alf          .
           perform   all-str-cen-000      thru all-str-cen-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-cnt-cor-pag-npa      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riempimento con '-'                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           inspect   w-cnt-cor-pag-npa
                                     replacing all " " by   "-"       .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      09                   to   v-car                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      37                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-cnt-cor-pag-npa    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       vis-cor-reg-npg-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-cor-reg-npg-999.
       vis-cor-reg-npg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione linea corpo numero : w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Abblencamento immagine linea di corpo           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-lin-imm              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero linea assoluta a video    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001
                                        giving w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003
                                     remainder w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-prc    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           add       w-lin-pri-lin-vid    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo visualizzazione riga               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig    =    "I"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-100
           else if   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig    =    "S"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-200
           else if   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig    =    "N"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-300
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-400.
       vis-lin-cor-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione indicatore linea         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "==>"                to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione numero linea a spaces    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione numero d'ordine riga     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rig-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione riga intera              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-405.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga in append : uscita              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rig-lst        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-lin-cor-999.
       vis-lin-cor-410.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing Numero d'ordine riga            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rig-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
       vis-lin-cor-415.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga di tipo New : fine editing      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        not  = spaces
                     go to vis-lin-cor-800.
       vis-lin-cor-450.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing segnale tipo riga reale         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
______*    if        w-rig-bld-rgb (1)    =    1
______*              move  "*"            to   w-lin-imm-seg-trr      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se le personalizzazioni prevedono l'ac- *
      *                      * cettazione dei 3 flag non bloccanti ed  *
      *                      * anche uno solo di questi e' diverso da  *
      *                      * spazi : segnale a video                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-sna-flg-nbr    =    spaces
                     go to vis-lin-cor-500.
      *
           if        w-prs-sna-flg-xbr (1)
                                          not  = spaces and
                     w-rig-flg-nbx (1, 1) not  = spaces
                     move  "*"            to   w-lin-imm-seg-trr      .
      *
           if        w-prs-sna-flg-xbr (2)
                                          not  = spaces and
                     w-rig-flg-nbx (1, 2) not  = spaces
                     move  "*"            to   w-lin-imm-seg-trr      .
      *
           if        w-prs-sna-flg-xbr (3)
                                          not  = spaces and
                     w-rig-flg-nbx (1, 3) not  = spaces
                     move  "*"            to   w-lin-imm-seg-trr      .
       vis-lin-cor-500.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing descrizione                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-502.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Deviazione a seconda del tipo riga  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "P" and
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tfu (1)
                                          =    spaces
                     go to vis-lin-cor-504
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-520.
       vis-lin-cor-504.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il tipo riga indica che si sta   *
      *                          * trattando un codice di magazzino    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Deviazione a seconda della per- *
      *                              * sonalizzazione di tipo esposi-  *
      *                              * zione descrizione               *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    00
                     go to vis-lin-cor-506
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    01
                     go to vis-lin-cor-508
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    02
                     go to vis-lin-cor-510
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    03
                     go to vis-lin-cor-512
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    04
                     go to vis-lin-cor-514
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    05
                     go to vis-lin-cor-516
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    06
                     go to vis-lin-cor-518
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-506.
       vis-lin-cor-506.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 00  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * A visualizzazione della so- *
      *                                  * la intera descrizione       *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-522.
       vis-lin-cor-508.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 01  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing primi 25 caratteri  *
      *                                  * della descrizione           *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d25-p01      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing codice magazzino    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-pro (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p01      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-524.
       vis-lin-cor-510.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 02  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing primi 21 caratteri  *
      *                                  * della descrizione           *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d21-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing parentesi sinistra  *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing tipo codice di ma-  *
      *                                  * gazzino                     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing parentesi destra    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing codice magazzino    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-pro (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-524.
       vis-lin-cor-512.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 03  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing codice magazzino    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-pro (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p03      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing primi 25 caratteri  *
      *                                  * della descrizione           *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d25-p03      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-524.
       vis-lin-cor-514.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 04  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing parentesi sinistra  *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p04      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing tipo codice di ma-  *
      *                                  * gazzino                     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p04      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing parentesi destra    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p04      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing codice magazzino    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-pro (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p04      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing primi 21 caratteri  *
      *                                  * della descrizione           *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-d21-p04      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-524.
       vis-lin-cor-516.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 05  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing codice magazzino    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-pro (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p01      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-524.
       vis-lin-cor-518.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se personalizzazione tipo : 06  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing parentesi sinistra  *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "["                  to   w-lin-imm-pqs-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing tipo codice di ma-  *
      *                                  * gazzino                     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    01
                     move  "P"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else if   w-rig-tip-mag (1)    =    03
                     move  "M"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02
           else      move  "?"            to   w-lin-imm-tco-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing parentesi destra    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "]"                  to   w-lin-imm-pqd-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing codice magazzino    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      w-rig-alf-pro (1)    to   w-lin-imm-cod-p02      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-524.
       vis-lin-cor-520.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il tipo riga indica che non si   *
      *                          * sta trattando un codice di magaz-   *
      *                          * zino                                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * A visualizzazione della sola    *
      *                              * intera descrizione              *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-522.
       vis-lin-cor-522.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Visualizzazione della sola in-  *
      *                              * tera descrizione                *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-der-rig (1, 1) to   w-lin-imm-des-rig      .
       vis-lin-cor-524.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Continuazione                   *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-550.
       vis-lin-cor-550.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing quantita' e prezzo              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Deviazione a seconda del tipo riga  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "A"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-575
           else if   w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "C"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-800
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-600.
       vis-lin-cor-575.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se tipo riga "A"                    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Editing dell'importo incolonna- *
      *                              * to con il prezzo                *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "GB"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-imp-rig (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-imp-aoa      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Continuazione                   *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-650.
       vis-lin-cor-600.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se tipo riga diverso da "A"         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Editing quantita'               *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   w-edt-qta-inc-ope      .
           move      w-rig-qta-ord (1)    to   w-edt-qta-inc-qta      .
           move      w-rig-dec-qta (1)    to   w-edt-qta-inc-dec      .
           move      "S"                  to   w-edt-qta-inc-sgn      .
           move      11                   to   w-edt-qta-inc-car      .
           perform   edt-qta-inc-000      thru edt-qta-inc-999        .
           move      w-edt-qta-inc-edt    to   w-lin-imm-qta-ord      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Editing segnale di valuta per   *
      *                              * il prezzo diversa da quella di  *
      *                              * fatturazione                    *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-sgl-vpp (1)    not  = w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)
                     move  "V"            to   w-lin-imm-sgn-vdf
           else      move  spaces         to   w-lin-imm-sgn-vdf      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Editing prezzo                  *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           if        w-rig-prz-ven (1)    >    9999999
                     move  09             to   v-car
           else      move  07             to   v-car                  .
           move      w-rig-dec-vpp (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           add       w-rig-dec-prz (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           if        w-rig-prz-ven (1)    >    9999999
                     move  "B"            to   v-edm
           else      move  "GB"           to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-prz-ven (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-prz-ven      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Continuazione                   *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-650.
       vis-lin-cor-650.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing importo                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-652.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Deviazione a seconda del tipo riga  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "P" and
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tfu (1)
                                          =    spaces
                     go to vis-lin-cor-654
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-660.
       vis-lin-cor-654.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il tipo riga indica che si sta   *
      *                          * trattando un codice di magazzino    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Deviazione a seconda della per- *
      *                              * sonalizzazione di tipo esposi-  *
      *                              * zione importo                   *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-rig-scr-imp    =    "I"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-656
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-imp    =    "C"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-658
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-imp    =    "S"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-659
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-656.
       vis-lin-cor-656.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se la personalizzazione indica  *
      *                              * l'esposizione dell'importo      *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Ad editing importo          *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-662.
       vis-lin-cor-658.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se la personalizzazione indica  *
      *                              * l'esposizione della data di     *
      *                              * consegna                        *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing data di consegna    *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-rig-dcn-ric (1)    to   v-dat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-imp-dtc      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-670.
       vis-lin-cor-659.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se la personalizzazione indica  *
      *                              * l'esposizione degli sconti      *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing sconto 1            *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      01                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<BD"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-per-scr (1, 1) to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Concatenamento sconto 1     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-imp-scr      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing sconto 2            *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      01                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<BD"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-per-scr (1, 2) to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Concatenamento sconto 2     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      02                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      13                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-lin-imm-imp-scr    to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           perform   all-str-csb-000      thru all-str-csb-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-lin-imm-imp-scr      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing sconto 3            *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      01                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<BD"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-per-scr (1, 3) to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Concatenamento sconto 3     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      02                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      13                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-lin-imm-imp-scr    to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           perform   all-str-csb-000      thru all-str-csb-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-lin-imm-imp-scr      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing sconto 4            *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      01                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<BD"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-per-scr (1, 4) to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Concatenamento sconto 4     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      02                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      13                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-lin-imm-imp-scr    to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           perform   all-str-csb-000      thru all-str-csb-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-lin-imm-imp-scr      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Editing sconto 5            *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      01                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<BD"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-per-scr (1, 5) to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Concatenamento sconto 5     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      02                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      13                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-lin-imm-imp-scr    to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           perform   all-str-csb-000      thru all-str-csb-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-lin-imm-imp-scr      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Continuazione               *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-670.
       vis-lin-cor-660.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il tipo riga indica che non si   *
      *                          * sta trattando un codice di magaz-   *
      *                          * zino                                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se il tipo riga e' "PN" : come  *
      *                              * per un codice di magazzino      *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "P" and
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tfu (1)
                                          =    "N"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-654.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se il tipo riga e' "A" : come   *
      *                              * per un codice di magazzino      *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "A"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-654.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Altrimenti : ad editing importo *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-662.
       vis-lin-cor-662.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Editing importo                     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-cor-664.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Deviazione a seconda del tipo   *
      *                              * riga                            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "A"
                     go to vis-lin-cor-666
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-668.
       vis-lin-cor-666.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se tipo riga "A" : nessun edi-  *
      *                              * ting dell'importo, in quanto    *
      *                              * gia' eseguito nella colonna     *
      *                              * per il prezzo                   *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-670.
       vis-lin-cor-668.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se tipo riga diverso da "A" si  *
      *                              * edita l'importo                 *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           if        w-rig-imp-rig (1)    >    9999999999 or
                     w-rig-imp-rig (1)    <   -9999999999
                     move  11             to   v-car
           else      move  09             to   v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           if        w-rig-imp-rig (1)    >    9999999999 or
                     w-rig-imp-rig (1)    <   -9999999999
                     move  "B"            to   v-edm
           else      move  "GB"           to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-rig-imp-rig (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-lin-imm-imp-rig      .
       vis-lin-cor-670.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Continuazione                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-lin-cor-800.
       vis-lin-cor-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Parametri per visualizzazione           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
       vis-lin-cor-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione visualizzazione prima linea          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-lin-imm-dsp-lin (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se una sola linea : uscita                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-num-lin-prc    =    1
                     go to vis-lin-cor-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione visualizzazione altre linee          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003      .
       vis-lin-cor-925.
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003      .
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003    >    w-lin-num-lin-prc
                     go to vis-lin-cor-999.
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-lin-imm-dsp-lin
                    (w-cnt-wrk-ctr-003)   to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-925.
       vis-lin-cor-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts area linee di corpo               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-cor-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate sia dall'area per la fin- *
      *              * catura che dall'area delle righe effettive      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-cor-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero riga                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fincatura                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "N.R"                to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sottolineatura                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "---"                to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-cor-reg-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Descrizione                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-cor-reg-310.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione a seconda della personalizzazio- *
      *                  * di tipo esposizione della descrizione       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    00
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-320
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    01 or
                     w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    05
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-330
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    02 or
                     w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    06
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-340
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    03
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-350
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-des    =    04
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-360
           else      go to pmt-cor-reg-320.
       pmt-cor-reg-320.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : 00              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "              Descrizione               "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "----------------------------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-400.
       pmt-cor-reg-330.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : 01 oppure 05    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "       Descrizione            Codice    "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "------------------------- --------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-400.
       pmt-cor-reg-340.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : 02 oppure 06    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "     Descrizione            Codice      "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "--------------------- ------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-400.
       pmt-cor-reg-350.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : 03              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "    Codice            Descrizione       "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "-------------- -------------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-400.
       pmt-cor-reg-360.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : 04              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "      Codice            Descrizione     "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      05                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "------------------ ---------------------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-400.
       pmt-cor-reg-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Quantita' e prezzo                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Fincatura                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      21                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      46                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      " Quantita'   Prezzo  "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sottolineatura                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      21                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      46                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "---------- ----------"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-cor-reg-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-cor-reg-510.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione a seconda della personalizzazio- *
      *                  * di tipo esposizione dell'importo            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-rig-scr-imp    =    "I"
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-520
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-imp    =    "C"
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-530
           else if   w-prs-rig-scr-imp    =    "S"
                     go to pmt-cor-reg-540
           else      go to pmt-cor-reg-520.
       pmt-cor-reg-520.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : "I"             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      68                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "   Importo   "      to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      68                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "-------------"      to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-600.
       pmt-cor-reg-530.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : "C"             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      68                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Data consegna"      to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      68                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "-------------"      to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-600.
       pmt-cor-reg-540.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se personalizzazione tipo : "S"             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fincatura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      68                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "   Sconti    "      to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      68                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "-------------"      to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-cor-reg-600.
       pmt-cor-reg-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattini di chiusura                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      all "-"              to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-cor-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione riga corpo di accettazione in w-rig       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-rig-cor-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se fase di duplicazioone riga precedente : si   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rig    =    "4"
                     go to vis-rig-cor-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se riga di tipo New : nessuna visualizzazione,  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        not  = spaces
                     go to vis-rig-cor-999.
       vis-rig-cor-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo riga                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tip-rig-000      thru vis-tip-rig-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice addebito o commento                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cod-aoc-000      thru vis-cod-aoc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice prodotto                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cod-pro-000      thru vis-cod-pro-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice prodotto secondo il cliente              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cop-scl-000      thru vis-cop-scl-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Descrizione riga                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-des-rig-000      thru vis-des-rig-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Quantita' ordinata                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-qta-ord-000      thru vis-qta-ord-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Seconda quantita'                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-qta-a02-000      thru vis-qta-a02-999        .
       vis-rig-cor-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo archivio                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-arc (1)    =    "D"
                     go to vis-rig-cor-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag non bloccante 1                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-flg-xb1-000      thru vis-flg-xb1-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag non bloccante 2                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-flg-xb2-000      thru vis-flg-xb2-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag non bloccante 3                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-flg-xb3-000      thru vis-flg-xb3-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Quantita' per confezione                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-qta-cfz-000      thru vis-qta-cfz-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Unita' di misura                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-umi-ven-000      thru vis-umi-ven-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sigla valuta per il prezzo                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-sgl-vpp-000      thru vis-sgl-vpp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Prezzo di vendita                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-prz-ven-000      thru vis-prz-ven-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lotto di vendita                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-lot-ven-000      thru vis-lot-ven-999        .
