      *                  * Visualizzazione prompt                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-flg-xb2-000      thru pmt-flg-xb2-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione valore                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-flg-xb2-000      thru vis-flg-xb2-999        .
       acc-flg-xb2-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rig-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rig-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rig-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rig
                             go to acc-flg-xb2-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rig-flg
                             go to acc-flg-xb2-100.
       acc-flg-xb2-999.
           exit.

