      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rig
                     go to acc-flg-xb3-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Pf4 : come Down                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "[4] "
                     move  "DOWN"         to   v-key                  .
